@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### ZETTELS MODULE - Knowledge Nodes
### ============================================

### ZETTELS - List Zettels
GET {{baseUrl}}/zettels?page=1&limit=20&search=typescript
Authorization: {{token}}

### ZETTELS - Get Zettel
GET {{baseUrl}}/zettels/:zettelId
Authorization: {{token}}

### ZETTELS - Create Zettel
POST {{baseUrl}}/zettels
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Database Optimization Techniques",
  "content": "Understanding database optimization strategies...",
  "tags": ["database", "performance", "optimization"]
}

### ZETTELS - Update Zettel
PUT {{baseUrl}}/zettels/:zettelId
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Database Optimization Techniques - Updated",
  "content": "Enhanced content with more examples..."
}

### ZETTELS - Delete Zettel
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/zettels/:zettelId
Authorization: {{token}}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Zettels are interconnected knowledge nodes
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
